This paper involves natural language generation and machine learning, which are common topics in the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of recurrent neural networks and attention mechanisms also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves data management and retrieval from Wikidata, which could fall under the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Databases (cs.DB).
